{"tid":2085252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"畢咗業一年 覺得人生無咩意義 好想死","createTime":"2020-06-29T19:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:02:30.000Z","uid":287274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c866278fff343eef9b80660621bf2158921cb3","tid":2085252,"uid":287274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"今日第一日返新工<br />\n連續兩日都失眠 好辛苦<br />\n唔知點解返親工都會好大壓力。。<br />\n明明自己只係一個small potato<br />\n可能未習慣或者做緊嘅唔係自己鍾意做嘅嘢<br />\n為生活點都要頂硬上<br />\n<br />\n只係想呻吓<br />\n但已經feel到自己情緒上有少少問題<br />\n好驚唔知幾時會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4dc355c707be7774c66b90c871940464392ebf","tid":2085252,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:13:36.000Z","msg":"點解咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786d7eadf820ff8c779abe1493d38bec23bdee58","tid":2085252,"uid":287274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4dc355c707be7774c66b90c871940464392ebf","tid":2085252,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:13:36.000Z","msg":"點解咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:17:26.000Z","msg":"我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能新環境掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186f723735f19717b311cd728fe1ed95a42167e4","tid":2085252,"uid":173133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:21:13.000Z","msg":"加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岩岩轉換新環境冇壓力就假既 唔洗擔心<br />\n我同你一樣轉左份新工 雖然公司樣樣野都好 但好似跳唔出comfort zone搞到好想quit<br />\n<br />\n不過諗諗吓 返工草埋草埋啲錢可以比自己做以前想做但冇錢做既野 個人會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上返新工我覺得都係推緊自己進步同成長 將來做得好都會有成就感架 一齊屌住啦"},{"pid":"b5ed324bcfd01d60593a73cd58b0654e28f3eb73","tid":2085252,"uid":296018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c866278fff343eef9b80660621bf2158921cb3","tid":2085252,"uid":287274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"今日第一日返新工<br />\n連續兩日都失眠 好辛苦<br />\n唔知點解返親工都會好大壓力。。<br />\n明明自己只係一個small potato<br />\n可能未習慣或者做緊嘅唔係自己鍾意做嘅嘢<br />\n為生活點都要頂硬上<br />\n<br />\n只係想呻吓<br />\n但已經feel到自己情緒上有少少問題<br />\n好驚唔知幾時會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:27:39.000Z","msg":"有這種感覺很正常<br />\n喺起步階段一定要 堅持 撐落去<br />\n相信我你一定頂得住<br />\n<br />\n但是 要記住 工作重要 但只是人生的一小部分<br />\n盡力去做突破自己固然重要 但係 都要留返啲空間畀自己抖下氣<br />\n<br />\n得閒留意下其他機會發掘 一啲你覺得有興趣嘅 方向"},{"pid":"9b28e1789c0566ef9f5c6ee0b98e8677ad270a19","tid":2085252,"uid":287274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186f723735f19717b311cd728fe1ed95a42167e4","tid":2085252,"uid":173133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:21:13.000Z","msg":"加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岩岩轉換新環境冇壓力就假既 唔洗擔心<br />\n我同你一樣轉左份新工 雖然公司樣樣野都好 但好似跳唔出comfort zone搞到好想quit<br />\n<br />\n不過諗諗吓 返工草埋草埋啲錢可以比自己做以前想做但冇錢做既野 個人會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上返新工我覺得都係推緊自己進步同成長 將來做得好都會有成就感架 一齊屌住啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:27:52.000Z","msg":"多謝你啊 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過跳出comfort zone真係唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29583ae736a13c440000c3ee863af6d20557c5b4","tid":2085252,"uid":287274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5ed324bcfd01d60593a73cd58b0654e28f3eb73","tid":2085252,"uid":296018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c866278fff343eef9b80660621bf2158921cb3","tid":2085252,"u